      "widgets_values": [
        "Replace the woman's gray short-sleeved dress with a beautiful and distinctive peacock-blue modern Chinese-style dress.\n\nThe new dress is made of silk satin with a subtle gradient from peacock blue to deep teal and a refined natural sheen. It features a small structured Mandarin collar, an elegant asymmetrical diagonal front, and three delicate white-jade frog buttons. Add short cape sleeves made of smoky blue organza, with sparse and finely embroidered silver-gold ginkgo leaves along the sleeve edges. The waist has clean, fitted tailoring. The overall design is elegant, refined, fashionable, and inspired by modern Eastern couture.\n\nMake the new garment fit her current pose naturally. Maintain physically correct contact and occlusion between the clothing, shoulders, arms, hands, and hair. Match the garment folds, highlights, and shadows to the original lighting.\n\nPreserve the woman's identity, face, facial features, skin tone, makeup, expression, hairstyle, hair color, body proportions, pose, hand positions, and gaze. Preserve the original background, lighting, camera angle, depth of field, framing, and composition.\n\nChange only the clothing. Keep everything else exactly the same."
      ]
